- Trademark : {{ $matter->titles->first()->value }}
- Number : {{ $matter->filing->detail }}
- Country : {{ $matter->countryInfo->name }}
- Registration date : {{ $matter->grant->event_date->isoFormat('LL') }}

Please find enclosed the registration certificate.

This trademark shall be renewed before {{ $matter->renewalsPending[0]->due_date->isoFormat('LL') }}. We will send you a reminder in due time.

Kind regards,

Hello,

