- Date of publication : {{ $matter->publication->event_date->isoFormat('LL') }}

Third parties can file an opposition before {{ $matter->tasks->where('code', 'WAT')->first()->due_date->isoFormat('LL') }}. When the opposition deadline expires, and if no opposition is filed, the Office will register the trademark. We will send you the registration certificate upon receipt.

<b>Warning</b> : You may receive letters from companies presenting themselves as official entities in the field of intellectual property, requesting payment for the publication of your trademark in their registers. This is a scam, and you should, of course, not respond to it. If you have any doubts, please do not hesitate to contact us.

<b>If your are an Amazon Seller</b> : You can now add your trademark to the <i>Amazon Brand Registry</i>. You will need to provide the name (or logo), select the trademark office where it was registered, and enter your trademark registration number. Amazon will then proceed with a verification process and may send us a confirmation code. We will forward this code to you upon receipt, allowing you to complete the process. Should you need any assistance with this registration, we are here to help.

Kind regards,

